#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.44"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.44:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.44:0.2"
msgid "5. Mahāyaññavagga"
msgstr "5. A Great Sacrifice"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 44. Sattaviññāṇaṭṭhitisutta → viññaṇaṭṭhitisuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Sattaviññāṇaṭṭhitisutta"
msgstr "44. Planes of Consciousness"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.44:1.1"
msgid "“Sattimā, bhikkhave, viññāṇaṭṭhitiyo."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these seven planes of consciousness."

msgctxt "an7.44:1.2"
msgid "Katamā satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.44:1.3"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, sattā nānattakāyā nānattasaññino, seyyathāpi manussā, "
"ekacce ca devā, ekacce ca vinipātikā."
msgstr ""
"There are sentient beings that are diverse in body and diverse in "
"perception, such as human beings, some gods, and some beings in the "
"underworld."

msgctxt "an7.44:1.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ paṭhamā viññāṇaṭṭhiti. (1)"
msgstr "This is the first plane of consciousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.40"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.44:2.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, sattā nānattakāyā ekattasaññino, seyyathāpi devā "
"brahmakāyikā paṭhamābhinibbattā."
msgstr ""
"There are sentient beings that are diverse in body and unified in "
"perception, such as the gods reborn in Brahmā’s Group through the first "
"absorption."

msgctxt "an7.44:2.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ dutiyā viññāṇaṭṭhiti. (2)"
msgstr "This is the second plane of consciousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.44:3.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, sattā ekattakāyā nānattasaññino, seyyathāpi devā ābhassarā."
msgstr ""
"There are sentient beings that are unified in body and diverse in "
"perception, such as the gods of streaming radiance."

msgctxt "an7.44:3.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ tatiyā viññāṇaṭṭhiti. (3)"
msgstr "This is the third plane of consciousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an7.44:4.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, sattā ekattakāyā ekattasaññino, seyyathāpi devā subhakiṇhā."
msgstr ""
"There are sentient beings that are unified in body and unified in "
"perception, such as the gods replete with glory."

msgctxt "an7.44:4.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ catutthā viññāṇaṭṭhiti. (4)"
msgstr "This is the fourth plane of consciousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an7.44:5.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, sattā sabbaso rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā paṭighasaññānaṃ "
"atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṃ amanasikārā ‘ananto ākāso’ti ākāsānañcāyatanūpagā."
msgstr ""
"There are sentient beings that have gone totally beyond perceptions of form. "
"With the ending of perceptions of impingement, not focusing on perceptions "
"of diversity, aware that ‘space is infinite’, they have been reborn in the "
"dimension of infinite space."

msgctxt "an7.44:5.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ pañcamā viññāṇaṭṭhiti. (5)"
msgstr "This is the fifth plane of consciousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an7.44:6.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, sattā sabbaso ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma ‘anantaṃ "
"viññāṇan’ti viññāṇañcāyatanūpagā."
msgstr ""
"There are sentient beings that have gone totally beyond the dimension of "
"infinite space. Aware that ‘consciousness is infinite’, they have been "
"reborn in the dimension of infinite consciousness."

msgctxt "an7.44:6.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ chaṭṭhā viññāṇaṭṭhiti. (6)"
msgstr "This is the sixth plane of consciousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an7.44:7.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, sattā sabbaso viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma ‘natthi kiñcī’"
"ti ākiñcaññāyatanūpagā."
msgstr ""
"There are sentient beings that have gone totally beyond the dimension of "
"infinite consciousness. Aware that ‘there is nothing at all’, they have been "
"reborn in the dimension of nothingness."

msgctxt "an7.44:7.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ sattamā viññāṇaṭṭhiti. (7)"
msgstr "This is the seventh plane of consciousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an7.44:8.1"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, satta viññāṇaṭṭhitiyo”ti."
msgstr "These are the seven planes of consciousness.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.44:8.2"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
